{"tid":380597,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一定取消餅卡政策　興德新校長：食得多都厭","createTime":"2017-08-30T08:42:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-31T04:35:01.000Z","uid":20058,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"be5249ad592b4cf05874c8a18c6104a301cf3467","tid":380597,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T08:42:20.000Z","msg":"屯門興德學校被爆出管理不善，偽造文件等醜聞，包括老師請病假要交出6張餅卡。前校長陳章萍被罷免，該校校董會今(30日)聘請新校長蕭麗珊，並於9月1日履新。被問到上任後會否取消教師請病假需交6張餅卡的政策，蕭回應指：「食得多都厭」，故一定會取消，強調病不是問題。 <br />\n<br />\n至於北上招生方面，她坦言，過往屯門及天水圍學校都有收生壓力，面對殺校危機時確實需要北上招生，但需視乎同事的意願，目前會着力本地招生。 <br />\n<br />\n校董雷其昌則指，目前學校有51名教師，已無分兩派，認為是51派，因每個人均是獨立，但整體而言仍是一派，希望老師集中精神教好學生，聚焦幫助學生進度，保證會愈做愈好，強調學校行政上無問題，亂已經是過去式。 <br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170830/mobile/bkn-20170830133338966-0830_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170830%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20170830133338966-0830_00822_001.html&d=aWzQphCdQ9hvhNqQQHhWEQKEmdudW1rq3V1Y15kzxIU%3D&h=45779922\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170830/mobile/bkn-20170830133338966-0830_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"245727c72ea301835c424ac659068272adfa2271","tid":380597,"uid":29080,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T08:44:05.000Z","msg":"起碼都請食炸脾la diu"},{"pid":"35184952b136efc1c36aa9c2b7f3e4aedfab8147","tid":380597,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T08:44:55.000Z","msg":"笑死<br />\n校董們舊時幾亂你地唔知？<br />\n而家出黎執行正義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4aca1faad5b1c3b0771a5d3acd6477873eb4bf81","tid":380597,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T08:46:20.000Z","msg":"食第二樣"},{"pid":"e66dab9a0073978980c64ae9b93156620f97722b","